Short: Enables a party to provide information on inventory levels
Definition: This is the logical model for the Inventory Status report - an information about the current status of a given inventory position. This is to be typically used in inventory counts - physical counts or estimates. It supports a report per status, per location, or a combination of both (which is how typically items are counted and reported).
